### Get a dev token (HS256) — available only in dev profile
GET http://localhost:8080/dev/token

### Call protected endpoint with the token
POST http://localhost:8080/secure/echo
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: text/plain

Привіт світ

### How to use
# 1) Start app in dev:  mvnw quarkus:dev
# 2) Run the first request to get a token and copy it to {{TOKEN}}
# 3) Run the POST request — expect: user=alice; received=Привіт світ
